Subject: [PATCH] selftests/net: synchronize udpgro tests' tx and rx connection
References: bsc#1218260
Patch-mainline: 6.6.34
Git-commit: 3bdd9fd29cb0f136b307559a19c107210ad5c314

From: Lucas Karpinski <lkarpins@redhat.com>

commit 3bdd9fd29cb0f136b307559a19c107210ad5c314 upstream.

The sockets used by udpgso_bench_tx aren't always ready when
udpgso_bench_tx transmits packets. This issue is more prevalent in -rt
kernels, but can occur in both. Replace the hacky sleep calls with a
function that checks whether the ports in the namespace are ready for
use.

